.top-note Deactivation / Renewal Emails of your <strong>I Done This</strong> account.

.content
  .header
    .main-wrap
      %table
        %tr
          %td
            %h1= 'Account Deactivation / Renewal Emails'

  .main
    .main-wrap
      .important-text
        %p Your <strong>I Done this</strong> account will be deactivated in 5 Days.

      .call-to-action
        %a.call-to-action_button{href: "https://#{ Rails.env.production? ? 'app.idonethis.com' : 'localhost:5000' }/"} Log in

      %p It looks like you haven't subscribed to any plan from past 2 months, <strong>I Done this</strong> accounts
        will be deactivated and all the data will be deleted from I Done This server after 5 days from now, You are
        requested to subscribe to any of the plan.

      %p Need help? email us at support@idonethis.com

  .footer
    %p.centered
      = link_to root_url do
        = image_tag "emails/we-love-progress.png", class: 'strapline', alt: 'We love progress'
